{"id":160613,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2011/06/澳广-越南积极加强海空军力/","date":"2011-06-13T06:00:17Z","modified":"2011-06-13T17:04:36Z","title":"澳广 | 越南积极加强海空军力","content":"<div>\n<p>越南积极加强海空军力</p>\n<p>越南近期积极加强海军与空军的军力，致力于装备现代化，采购高科技武器，建设防空与侦察系统。.</p>\n<div>\n<div>\n<div>\n<table cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" border=\"0\">\n<tr>\n<td>\n<div>\n<p>2011 年 06 月 13 日</p>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.radioaustralia.net.au/chinese/articles/s3242290.htm\"><img src=\"http://www.radioaustralia.net.au/chinese/img/icons/decrease.gif\" alt=\"Decrease\" title=\"Decrease\" /></a> <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.radioaustralia.net.au/chinese/articles/s3242290.htm\"><img src=\"http://www.radioaustralia.net.au/chinese/img/icons/standard.gif\" alt=\"Standard\" title=\"Standard\" /></a> <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.radioaustralia.net.au/chinese/articles/s3242290.htm\"><img src=\"http://www.radioaustralia.net.au/chinese/img/icons/increase.gif\" alt=\"Increase\" title=\"Increase\" /></a> | <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.abc.net.au/cgi-bin/common/mailto/mailto-nojs_query.pl?http://www.abc.net.au/ra/chinese/articles/s3242290.htm&#038;presname=/ra\"><img src=\"http://www.radioaustralia.net.au/chinese/img/icons/email.gif\" alt=\"Email\" title=\"Email\" /></a> | <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.abc.net.au/cgi-bin/common/printfriendly.pl?http://www.abc.net.au/ra/chinese/articles/s3242290.htm\"><img src=\"http://www.radioaustralia.net.au/chinese/img/icons/print.gif\" alt=\"Print\" title=\"Print\" /></a> | <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.radioaustralia.net.au/chinese/articles/s3242290.htm\"><img src=\"http://www.radioaustralia.net.au/chinese/img/icons/favourite.gif\" alt=\"Favourite\" title=\"Favourite\" /></a></p>\n<p>越南近期积极加强海军与空军的军力，致力于装备现代化，采购高科技武器，建设防空与侦察系统。</p>\n<p>根据越南国防部2011至2015年年的建军计划，提高军队与国防工业力量是当务之急。<br />2011年越南的国防预算约达26亿美元，比去年增加70％。越南希望国内企业积极参加军队现代化的建设。</p>\n<p>越南为保领海的和平与渔民的安全，已支出一大笔经费，增添海军装备，提高海军作战能力。</p>\n</div>\n</td